{{SupportPage|vendor=NETGEAR|model=WNHDE111|vs_id=2613}} [http://www.dd-wrt.com/phpBB2/viewtopic.php?p=206552 On the DD-WRT forums] (internal shots) :"2976302702" is silkscreened on the board. The IP address in AP mode defaults to 192.168.0.240. The IP address in Bridge mode defaults to 192.168.0.241. Per the manual, the default SSID is '''NETGEAR-HD'''. Appears to be using 2 chains for TX and RX, 3 antennas
